---
// Section targeting orthodontists
---

<section id="orthodontists" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-brand-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 text-brand-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
          </svg>
          Para profesionales
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          Recomendá <span class="text-brand-300">Keep Aligned</span> a tus pacientes
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-brand-200 mb-8">
          Ayudá a tus pacientes a mantener el compromiso con su tratamiento de ortodoncia invisible. 
          Una app gratuita que mejora la adherencia y los resultados.
        </p>

        <!-- Benefits -->
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-success-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-success-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Mayor adherencia al tratamiento</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm">Los pacientes que trackean sus horas tienen un 40% más de probabilidad de cumplir las 22 horas diarias recomendadas.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-success-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-success-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Pacientes más comprometidos</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm">La gamificación y el seguimiento visual mantienen a los pacientes motivados durante todo el tratamiento.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-success-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-success-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Mejores resultados clínicos</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm">Un tratamiento consistente significa movimientos dentales predecibles y tiempos de tratamiento optimizados.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a 
            href="mailto:agustinarone@gmail.com?subject=Keep Aligned para mi clínica" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-brand-900 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all hover:bg-brand-50 hover:shadow-lg"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            Contactar
          </a>
          <a 
            href="#download" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/10 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all hover:bg-white/20 border border-white/20"
          >
            Descargar para probar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Stats cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">40%</div>
            <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm">Mayor cumplimiento de horas diarias</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">22h</div>
            <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm">Meta diaria trackeable</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">100%</div>
            <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm">Gratis para pacientes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">iOS</div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">&amp; Android</div>
            <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm">Disponible en ambas plataformas</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Coming soon badge -->
        <div class="mt-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-600 to-brand-500 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-brand-400/30">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Versión Premium para Clínicas</h4>
                <span class="text-[10px] bg-warning-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium">Próximamente</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-brand-200 text-sm">Dashboard para monitorear el progreso de tus pacientes de forma remota.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

